      <h2>Method</h2>

<h3>Surveys</h3>

<p>One of the best ways to&nbsp;assess current and future trip generation is to survey current movements at the same site or somewhere similar. You can use information on how people travel&nbsp;now to predict how people will travel&nbsp;in future.</p>

<p>If possible, you should also survey all the current delivery and servicing movements to and from the site.</p>

<p>See survey instructions and use our data collection template:</p>
      
           
      
