<p>If you want to use another method for trip generation, or other data sources and decisions for mode share, your assessment approach should be approved by us through our <a href="/info-for/urban-planning-and-construction/planning-applications/pre-application-services">pre-application services</a>. You must explain and justify it in your <a href="/info-for/urban-planning-and-construction/transport-assessment-guide/transport-assessments">Transport Assessment</a>.</p>
